
# tap repositories and their packages

## caskroom/cask
tap caskroom/cask
install brew-cask

cask install xquartz #/Applications/Utilities/XQuartz.app

## phinze/cask
tap phinze/cask

## rcmdnk/file
tap rcmdnk/file
install brew-file

